  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_20_11247-11322",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "11247-11322",
      "markText": "那封信只有死亡才能摧毁。没有灰烬留下。死亡回到床上，搂住那个男人，她也不知道自己是怎么了，从不睡觉的她感到睡意轻轻拉下了她的眼皮。第二天，没有人死去。",
      "totalCount": 1314,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=11247&rangeEnd=11322",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=11247&rangeEnd=11322"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_12_10876-10907",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "10876-10907",
      "markText": "晚上十一点五十九分，主席心脏病发作。午夜最后一声钟响，他死了。",
      "totalCount": 1144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=10876&rangeEnd=10907",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=10876&rangeEnd=10907"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_6_2509-2588",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2509-2588",
      "markText": "这会造成令人不安的后果，一场运动应运而生，参与的民众坚定地相信，仅仅通过意志力的作用，死亡是可以战胜的，所以，先前的祖祖辈辈枉然离世，都可被诟病为意志力薄弱。",
      "totalCount": 828,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2509&rangeEnd=2588",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2509&rangeEnd=2588"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_16_6502-6556",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "6502-6556",
      "markText": "死亡坐在角落里自己看着。过了很久，狗从毯子上站起来，跳到沙发上。死亡生平第一次体会到，怀里有只狗是什么感觉。",
      "totalCount": 594,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=6502&rangeEnd=6556",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=6502&rangeEnd=6556"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_10_8065-8112",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "8065-8112",
      "markText": "依照第二十六页的事例，死者都是自愿赴死的，所以在死亡证明上，死因将登记为自杀。水龙头又打开了。",
      "totalCount": 555,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8065&rangeEnd=8112",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8065&rangeEnd=8112"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_6_402-412",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "402-412",
      "markText": "第二天，没有人死去。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=402&rangeEnd=412",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=402&rangeEnd=412"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_8_931-981",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "931-981",
      "markText": "无论我们兜多少圈子，宗教，所有的宗教，离了死亡就都没了存在的理由，宗教需要死亡就像口腹需要面包一样。",
      "totalCount": 465,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=931&rangeEnd=981",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=931&rangeEnd=981"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_5_484-564",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "484-564",
      "markText": "比如当你更深入地思考死亡，如果你没有就此发现新的形象、新的语言界限，那实在不正常。 ——维特根斯坦",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=484&rangeEnd=564",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=484&rangeEnd=564"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_16_4141-4175",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "4141-4175",
      "markText": "这会是个不错的由头，让某人在另一本书的开头写道：第二天，没有狗死去。",
      "totalCount": 425,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4141&rangeEnd=4175",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=4141&rangeEnd=4175"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_10_493-564",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "493-564",
      "markText": "不幸的是，当人要盲目穿越现实政治的泥沼之地，当实用主义接过指挥棒，罔顾乐谱上的音符肆意指挥，卑鄙的铁律必将昭示，仍然有堕落的阶梯可供逐级而下。",
      "totalCount": 414,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=493&rangeEnd=564",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=493&rangeEnd=564"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_7_2459-2523",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2459-2523",
      "markText": "特此建议政府强制规定，所有自然死亡或卒于意外的宠物，必须举办土葬或火化，土葬、火化必须一律符合章程、获得批准，并由丧葬行业承办。",
      "totalCount": 405,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2459&rangeEnd=2523",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2459&rangeEnd=2523"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300034708_6_489-550",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "489-550",
      "markText": "一整天过去，二十四小时的挥霍，白昼黑夜，日出日落，没有一场抱病而终，没有一回失足坠亡，没有一桩成功自杀，没有，什么也没有。",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300034708&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=489&rangeEnd=550",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fea32ff0813ab740eg01829e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=489&rangeEnd=550"
    },
    {
